{{#eq object 'boss2-lackey1'}}
  <p>An office worker sits at his desk. He has a pile of papers on his
  desk.</p>

  <blockquote>
    <p>Are you going in there to fight our boss? Good luck with that.</p>
  </blockquote>
{{else eq object 'boss2-lackey2'}}
  <p>An office worker is intently focused on his work.</p>

  <blockquote>
    <p>&hellip;</p>
    <p>Who are you? Why are you bothering me? It's times like these I wish I
    could just close my door.</p>
  </blockquote>
{{else eq object 'boss2-lackey3'}}
  <p>An office worker pretends to work, but his screen is clearly showing Reddit.</p>

  <blockquote>
    <p>Huh, are you here for the boss man? He's just through that open door.</p>
  </blockquote>
{{else eq object 'boss2'}}
  {{#unless state.beatBoss2}}
  <p>Boss 2 fights you!</p>
  {{else}}
  {{! already beat boss }}
  <blockquote>
  <p>Ok, you beat me. I've opened the backdoor, which will let you go ahead.
  You better steer clear of the folk in the next area &mdash; they're quite
  dangerous, much more so than me.</p>
  </blockquote>
  {{/unless}}
{{else}}
  {{> notfound}}
{{/eq}}
